
<p>(c) The two Sacraments ordained by Christ Himself&mdash;Baptism and the<br/>Supper of the Lord&mdash;ministered with unfailing use of Christ's words of<br/>Institution, and of the elements ordained by Him.</p>
<p>4.  The Historic Episcopate, locally adapted in the methods of its<br/>administration to the varying needs of the nations and peoples called of<br/>God into the Unity of His Church.</p>
    